Package it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws

This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaws and relatives.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ChemicalPattern<ExtenderType> This interface models a generic template which represents a component of an Ecolaw.
Ecolaw This interface represents an Ecolaw that is applied in the SAPERE ecosystem.
Filter This interface models a generic filter that will be applied to a ChemicalPattern.
Product This interface models a Product, which is a template for an LSA to be applies to an LSA-space.
Rate<Type> This interface represents the rate at which a reaction is triggered.
Reactant This interface models a Reactant, which is a template for an LSA to be matched in the LSA-space.
Term<Type> This interface models an Ecolaw Term, used in filters.
 

Package it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws Description

This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaws and relatives.
